name: carolyn_guay
tweet:
There are many ongoing clinical trials of ASOs, due in large part to their unique attributes:
- direct translation of genomic information
- can target any RNA (coding or noncoding)
- efficient drug development
- effects are titratable
- effects are long-acting, but reversible
